strings: <voice_0x01000ECF><se_low>*: Ah, if it isn't Prince Charmless<endash> I mean, Prince Charmles! I s'pose you must be 'ere for the initiation, then?
<voice_0x01000ED0><se_def>Prince Charmles: Indeed I am...you uneducated bumpkin.

<voice_0x01000ED1><se_low>*: Ah, ha ha! An' who's this with you, eh?
Last I heard, you royals had to go in alone...
<voice_0x01000ED2><se_def>Prince Charmles: They merely accompanied me here.
<voice_0x01000ED3><se_def>Prince Charmles: They shall be accompanying me on the way home as well. I've instructed them to await my return just inside the royal hunting ground.
<voice_0x01000ED4><se_low>*: Oh, right you are! Well I hope you have a good hunt then. I got to be gettin' on now...
<voice_0x01000ED7><se_low>*: Oh, right you are! Well I hope you have a good hunt then. I got to be<endash>
<voice_0x01000ED8><se_low>*: Oh no, you can't go like that...

<voice_0x01000ED5><se_low>*: I s'pose Your Highness knows this already, but them Argon lizards are shy beasts.
They'll run at the first whiff of a man.
<voice_0x01000ED9><se_low>*: You won't get no Argon hearts smelling like that, Your Highness! You want to cover that up with something!

<voice_0x01000ED6><se_low>*: You'll still need to take care, mind.
The only way to get close to them Argon
lizards is to sneak up behind them.
<voice_0x01000EDD><se_high>*: Ooh, hang on a mo. If you're off to the initiation, you'd better know your stuff about the old salamango! What you do is...

<voice_0x01000EDE><se_high>*: You hold it like this...
And then you throw it with all your might!

<voice_0x01000EDF><se_high>*: That'll break the skin, see.
Then you can get at the fruit inside.
Them Argon lizards can't get enough of it!

<voice_0x01000EE0><se_high>*: Just a sniff of one of these and
they're awake!
